  "reference_number": "MYA0044",
  "remarks": "\nThe Myanmar Armed Forces have a track record of committing serious human rights violations and violations of international humanitarian law in Myanmar for decades.\n \nJSC Gorizont is a Russian company which has been responsible for the supply and upkeep of aircraft for the Myanmar Armed Forces since the coup in February 2021. Therefore, JSC Gorizont has been and is involved in the supply of dual-use goods for the use of the Myanmar Armed Forces.\n",
